{"tid":610754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港政府：強烈譴責戴耀廷港獨言論","createTime":"2018-03-30T08:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T12:56:15.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"a9d9f3223e3424653081721ba364e39996c9cf26","tid":610754,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:52:47.000Z","msg":"港大法律學院教授戴耀廷近日在台灣一個論壇上，呼籲港人應該思考日後應成為獨立國家，還是與其他中華民族組成聯邦。<br />\n<br />\n有關言論連日被受左派報章炮轟，特區政府下午發聲明回應稱，對有大學教員發表有關香港可以考慮成立獨立國家的言論感到震驚，並予以強烈譴責，又重申任何有關「港獨」的主張，均不符合「一國兩制」、《基本法》以及香港社會的整體和長遠利益。"},{"pid":"d9c68df5fc0f84657a1e48812a2dc4b839d418b7","tid":610754,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:52:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201803/30/P2018033000531.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201803%2F30%2FP2018033000531.htm&d=IpqsRxaBTMs1a32MJNL3jP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=7d9481a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201803/30/P2018033000531.htm</a>"},{"pid":"acc20d5d86cc94bc5dbf102c70ba317f0498475f","tid":610754,"uid":49955,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:15:45.000Z","msg":"支持戴妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30bb852e3e9ca59de54f576b08838810bf5cf190","tid":610754,"uid":34869,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"咁都要出信回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e782ff2185628f0cee03f3fadebbd7a27cecdb7","tid":610754,"uid":162564,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:18:07.000Z","msg":"虛怯到"},{"pid":"de555f497f0f1d0a132d27529eb754b28cade91d","tid":610754,"uid":38671,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:19:34.000Z","msg":"戴耀廷已變港獨派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma