a372e1b30","tid":610754,"uid":16676,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:23:31.000Z","msg":"23條又未立<br />\n學術討論都要講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算人地係外地講藏獨又如何<br />\n講巴塞獨立唔通你又管 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"境外言論都要管？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T10:08:59.000Z","msg":"咁境外燒基本法會唔會冇得參選<br />\n境外宣傳結束一黨專政係咪又冇得做議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T11:37:20.000Z","msg":"境外燒國旗都唔犯法啦"},{"pid":"07eecebbf79576dc2f44927d5a70b721e64de4fb","tid":610754,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T11:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港共最終目的想清洗大學言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個都做個個堅持, 撚有得清洗言論自由呢回事"},{"pid":"803d0e75f50b8c20200d05267cb49f4852ba7fc9","tid":610754,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T11:42:31.000Z","msg":"戴耀廷回應<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BennyTaiHK/posts/849997688527327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBennyTaiHK%2Fposts%2F849997688527327&d=IpqsRxaBTMs1a32MJNL3jP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=49595746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BennyTaiHK/posts/849997688527327</a>"},{"pid":"28b2b28c6c49f0b88716abef0ec38bffc19cb2a3","tid":610754,"uid":138409,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"803d0e75f50b8c20200d05267cb49f4852ba7fc9","tid":610754,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T11:42:31.000Z","msg":"戴耀廷回應<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BennyTaiHK/posts/849997688527327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBennyTaiHK%2Fposts%2F849997688527327&d=IpqsRxaBTMs1a32MJNL3jP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=49595746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BennyTaiHK/posts/849997688527327</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T11:42:52.000Z","msg":"就特區政府對本人發出譴責的聲明<br />\n<br />\n特區政府發表聲明指我在台灣作出了有關香港可以考慮成立獨立國家的言論。政府發言人說：「特區政府對有大學教員發表有關香港可以考慮成立獨立國家的言論感到震驚，並予以強烈譴責。」 <br />\n特區政府在尚未了解事實就發表這樣的聲明，我在此表示極度失望。當天我在一個由台灣青年反共救國團舉辦有關「港澳中、各民族及台灣自由人權論壇」上，發表的言論重點如下：<br />\n一、 香港的民主運動應定位為反專制的運動。<br />\n二、 中國現在的專制政權有一天會結朿。<br />\n三、 中國必會成為一個民主的國家。<br />\n四、 到了那一天，香港人也能實現民主普選，並且可以實現「人民自決」。<br />\n五、 那時候，港人可考慮是否成立獨立國家，或與中國其他地區的族群組成聯邦或邦聯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%E2%80%A6&d=IpqsRxaBTMs1a32MJNL3jP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a6bc7239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch&hellip;</a><br />\n(本人發言從 3:00 到 5:00)<br />\n<br />\n這些言論我早在香港的報章上已曾發表過，並沒有甚麼新的觀點。現在特區政府在回應某些傳媒的查詢，這樣高調發表針對本人的聲明，令人懷疑特區政府是否為了在未來進行二十三條立法做勢，及打擊港人的言論自由，連討論及想像中國與香港的未來也會受到壓制。<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷"},{"pid":"1063eb07f02a55a9934e5b2e59f23fff7fe16225","tid":610754,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T11:44:02.000Z","msg":"戴妖其實係想組聯邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過對支那嚟講，聯邦一樣係港獨"},{"pid":"add64b3a94ef5b5a37ee46c4bc7696929d248ec9","tid":610754,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T11:50:13.000Z","msg":"咁都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 獨派小貓三四隻"},{"pid":"153e20c1f176a91f65dcb5df33f5467d75093e8a","tid":610754,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T11:55:08.000Z","msg":"二、 中國現在的專制政權有一天會結朿。<br />\n三、 中國必會成為一個民主的國家。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢兩點足夠屈你港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1066b474379da4dd1131619897a6ec411e920e7d","tid":6